to me either.

1260
01:01:04,094 --> 01:01:05,234
You can call it a lie.

1261
01:01:05,229 --> 01:01:07,129
I call it
a mental reservation.

1262
01:01:07,131 --> 01:01:08,701
A mental reservation?

1263
01:01:08,699 --> 01:01:10,169
