in a crowd.

1406
01:07:36,219 --> 01:07:38,249
With everybody
calling you a creep,

1407
01:07:38,255 --> 01:07:39,815
it's easy
to get confused.

1408
01:07:39,823 --> 01:07:41,623
Yeah, I guess.

1409
01:07:41,625 --> 01:07:43,625
It was probably
your imagination.

1410
01:07:43,627 --> 01:07:46,187
It is not my imagination!

1411
01:07:46,196 --> 01:07:48,096
